    "Thirdly, technical problems such as instability, slow response times, incomplete feedback (with portions of the question unanswered), and limited comprehension of the Chinese language were mentioned by 9 students.",
    "Concerning research question 4 (How do college students' perceptions of ChatGPT change following their experience with CFP mode?",
    "), we collected student responses via surveys and analyzed the data using T-tests to investigate the students' perspectives on ChatGPT.",
    "Using the T-test, this study identified some variations in the perception scores of CFP learners.",
    "The mean scores of the students on the pre-test and post-test for the factors comprising four sub-dimensions-\"perceived usefulness, perceived ease of use, intention to use, and attitude\"-are presented in Table 5."
